fulltitle: "Talk Across America" Guests Jazz Legend Dick Hyman and Actor/Singer Bill Hayes (Part 2)
title: "Talk Across America" Guests Jazz Legend Dick Hyman and Actor/Singer Bill Hayes (Part 2)
description:
Doug Miles talks with Legendary Jazz musician and composer Dick Hyman and actor/singer Bill Hayes "Days of Our Lives"  about the show they are opening at the Golden Apple Dinner Theatre in Sarasota, FL. Both men talk about their early days in television. Bill talks about the state of Soap Operas. Aired WSLR Radio/WTMY Radio. 
(Part 2) (www.dougmilesmedia.com)
